{"tid":882465,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果俾你生仔 你想佢係中文環境定英文環境成長？","createTime":"2018-10-30T06:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T22:52:24.000Z","uid":185572,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"274cdd0cdefda28628edf938024f41b759d082ce","tid":882465,"uid":185572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"我成日都諗一個問題<br />\n<br />\n啲用英文成長嘅國家<br />\n<br />\n一出世已經少左一個語言問題<br />\n<br />\n英文去邊都用到<br />\n<br />\n班美英澳鬼佬根本可以成世都唔洗學其他語言<br />\n<br />\n但啲其他母語嘅人就要用起碼十年先可以了解到英文<br />\n<br />\n要更深一步時間仲多<br />\n<br />\n搞到好似同班鬼佬比自己晒左好多時間係學好語言<br />\n<br />\n如果想個下一代好<br />\n<br />\n你會俾佢係香港成長定外國成長？<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英語國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ed9343ced51a41750744e9565bd5fe45410284","tid":882465,"uid":189719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72974dcab548b51f8319ba04393604d55abc65e6","tid":882465,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"廣話加英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0882ec42ce3462864da96f6d685089badf92ddfb","tid":882465,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T22:52:24.000Z","msg":"愈識得多就愈好啦<br />\n英廣普日韓"}]}